1 /********************************************************************
2 *
3 * Standard register and bit definitions for the Texas Instruments
4 * MSP430 microcontroller.
5 *
6 * This file supports assembler and C development for
7 * MSP430FR57XXGENERIC device.
8 *
9 * Texas Instruments, Version 1.0
10 *
11 * Rev. 1.0, Setup
12 *
13 *

27 #if (((__TID__ >> 8) & 0x7F) != 0x2b) /* 0x2b = 43 dec */

32 #ifdef __IAR_SYSTEMS_ICC__
33 #include "in430.h"
34 #pragma language=extended
35 
36 #define DEFC(name, address) __no_init volatile unsigned char name @ address;
37 #define DEFW(name, address) __no_init volatile unsigned short name @ address;
38 
39 #define DEFCW(name, address) __no_init union \
40 { \
41  struct \
42  { \
43  volatile unsigned char name##_L; \
44  volatile unsigned char name##_H; \
45  }; \
46  volatile unsigned short name; \
47 } @ address;
48 
49 #define READ_ONLY_DEFCW(name, address) __no_init union \
50 { \
51  struct \
52  { \
53  volatile READ_ONLY unsigned char name##_L; \
54  volatile READ_ONLY unsigned char name##_H; \
55  }; \
56  volatile READ_ONLY unsigned short name; \
57 } @ address;
58 
59 
60 #if __REGISTER_MODEL__ == __REGISTER_MODEL_REG20__
61 #define __ACCESS_20BIT_REG__ void __data20 * volatile
62 #else
63 #define __ACCESS_20BIT_REG__ volatile unsigned short /* only short access from C is allowed in small memory model */
64 #endif
65 
66 #define DEFA(name, address) __no_init union \
67 { \
68  struct \
69  { \
70  volatile unsigned char name##_L; \
71  volatile unsigned char name##_H; \
72  }; \
73  struct \
74  { \
75  volatile unsigned short name##L; \
76  volatile unsigned short name##H; \
77  }; \
78  __ACCESS_20BIT_REG__ name; \
79 } @ address;
80 
81 #endif /* __IAR_SYSTEMS_ICC__ */
82

84 #ifdef __IAR_SYSTEMS_ASM__
85 #define DEFC(name, address) sfrb name = address;
86 #define DEFW(name, address) sfrw name = address;
87 
88 #define DEFCW(name, address) sfrbw name, name##_L, name##_H, address;
89 sfrbw macro name, name_L, name_H, address;
90 sfrb name_L = address;
91 sfrb name_H = address+1;
92 sfrw name = address;
93  endm
94 
95 #define READ_ONLY_DEFCW(name, address) const_sfrbw name, name##_L, name##_H, address;
96 const_sfrbw macro name, name_L, name_H, address;
97 const sfrb name_L = address;
98 const sfrb name_H = address+1;
99 const sfrw name = address;
100  endm
101 
102 #define DEFA(name, address) sfrba name, name##L, name##H, name##_L, name##_H, address;
103 sfrba macro name, nameL, nameH, name_L, name_H, address;
104 sfrb name_L = address;
105 sfrb name_H = address+1;
106 sfrw nameL = address;
107 sfrw nameH = address+2;
108 sfrl name = address;
109  endm
110 
111 #endif /* __IAR_SYSTEMS_ASM__*/

156 #ifndef __IAR_SYSTEMS_ICC__ /* Begin #defines for assembler */
157 #define LPM0 (CPUOFF)
158 #define LPM1 (SCG0+CPUOFF)
159 #define LPM2 (SCG1+CPUOFF)
160 #define LPM3 (SCG1+SCG0+CPUOFF)
161 #define LPM4 (SCG1+SCG0+OSCOFF+CPUOFF)
162 /* End #defines for assembler */
163 
164 #else /* Begin #defines for C */
165 #define LPM0_bits (CPUOFF)
166 #define LPM1_bits (SCG0+CPUOFF)
167 #define LPM2_bits (SCG1+CPUOFF)
168 #define LPM3_bits (SCG1+SCG0+CPUOFF)
169 #define LPM4_bits (SCG1+SCG0+OSCOFF+CPUOFF)
170 
171 #include "in430.h"
172 
173 #if __MSP430_HEADER_VERSION__ < 1107
174 #define LPM0 _BIS_SR(LPM0_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 0 */
175 #define LPM0_EXIT _BIC_SR_IRQ(LPM0_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 0 */
176 #define LPM1 _BIS_SR(LPM1_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 1 */
177 #define LPM1_EXIT _BIC_SR_IRQ(LPM1_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 1 */
178 #define LPM2 _BIS_SR(LPM2_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 2 */
179 #define LPM2_EXIT _BIC_SR_IRQ(LPM2_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 2 */
180 #define LPM3 _BIS_SR(LPM3_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 3 */
181 #define LPM3_EXIT _BIC_SR_IRQ(LPM3_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 3 */
182 #define LPM4 _BIS_SR(LPM4_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 4 */
183 #define LPM4_EXIT _BIC_SR_IRQ(LPM4_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 4 */
184 #else
185 #define LPM0 __bis_SR_register(LPM0_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 0 */
186 #define LPM0_EXIT __bic_SR_register_on_exit(LPM0_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 0 */
187 #define LPM1 __bis_SR_register(LPM1_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 1 */
188 #define LPM1_EXIT __bic_SR_register_on_exit(LPM1_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 1 */
189 #define LPM2 __bis_SR_register(LPM2_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 2 */
190 #define LPM2_EXIT __bic_SR_register_on_exit(LPM2_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 2 */
191 #define LPM3 __bis_SR_register(LPM3_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 3 */
192 #define LPM3_EXIT __bic_SR_register_on_exit(LPM3_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 3 */
193 #define LPM4 __bis_SR_register(LPM4_bits) /* Enter Low Power Mode 4 */
194 #define LPM4_EXIT __bic_SR_register_on_exit(LPM4_bits) /* Exit Low Power Mode 4 */
195 #endif
196 #endif /* End #defines for C */

3999 #define WDTSSEL_1 (1*0x0020u) /* WDT - Timer Clock Source Select: ACLK */
4000 #define WDTSSEL_2 (2*0x0020u) /* WDT - Timer Clock Source Select: VLO_CLK */

4006 /* WDT-interval times [1ms] coded with Bits 0-2 */
4007 /* WDT is clocked by fSMCLK (assumed 1MHz) */
4008 #define WDT_MDLY_32 (WDTPW+WDTTMSEL+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2) /* 32ms interval (default) */
4009 #define WDT_MDLY_8 (WDTPW+WDTTMSEL+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTIS0) /* 8ms " */
4010 #define WDT_MDLY_0_5 (WDTPW+WDTTMSEL+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTIS1) /* 0.5ms " */
4011 #define WDT_MDLY_0_064 (WDTPW+WDTTMSEL+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTIS1+WDTIS0) /* 0.064ms " */
4012 /* WDT is clocked by fACLK (assumed 32KHz) */
4013 #define WDT_ADLY_1000 (WDTPW+WDTTMSEL+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTSSEL0) /* 1000ms " */
4014 #define WDT_ADLY_250 (WDTPW+WDTTMSEL+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTSSEL0+WDTIS0) /* 250ms " */
4015 #define WDT_ADLY_16 (WDTPW+WDTTMSEL+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTSSEL0+WDTIS1) /* 16ms " */
4016 #define WDT_ADLY_1_9 (WDTPW+WDTTMSEL+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTSSEL0+WDTIS1+WDTIS0) /* 1.9ms " */
4017 /* Watchdog mode -> reset after expired time */
4018 /* WDT is clocked by fSMCLK (assumed 1MHz) */
4019 #define WDT_MRST_32 (WDTPW+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2) /* 32ms interval (default) */
4020 #define WDT_MRST_8 (WDTPW+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTIS0) /* 8ms " */
4021 #define WDT_MRST_0_5 (WDTPW+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTIS1) /* 0.5ms " */
4022 #define WDT_MRST_0_064 (WDTPW+WDTCNTCL+WDTIS2+WDTIS1+WDTIS0) /* 0.064ms " */
4023 /* WDT is clocked by fACLK (assumed 32KHz) */
4024 #define WDT_ARST_1000 (WDTPW+WDTCNTCL+WDTSSEL0+WDTIS2) /* 1000ms " */
4025 #define WDT_ARST_250 (WDTPW+WDTCNTCL+WDTSSEL0+WDTIS2+WDTIS0) /* 250ms " */
4026 #define WDT_ARST_16 (WDTPW+WDTCNTCL+WDTSSEL0+WDTIS2+WDTIS1) /* 16ms " */
4027 #define WDT_ARST_1_9 (WDTPW+WDTCNTCL+WDTSSEL0+WDTIS2+WDTIS1+WDTIS0) /* 1.9ms " */
